SEVERABILITY

If any provision of this license is held to be unenforceable, such provision shall be reformed only to the extent necessary to make it enforceable, and the remainder of this license shall remain in full force and effect.

This license represents a social compact and community standard first, and a legal framework second. It is designed to encourage sharing while protecting creators from exploitation in modern digital environments.
